preibisch_imagelib2.img

Class ImagePlusAdapter

  • java.lang.Object
    • preibisch_imagelib2.img.ImagePlusAdapter

  • public class ImagePlusAdapter
extends Object
    Provides convenience functions to wrap ImageJ 1.x data structures as ImgLib2 ones, and vice versa.

    Author:
    Stephan Preibisch, Stephan Saalfeld
